Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小理濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再干下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…喂  理濑！
